{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">It all started with a murder...</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086690/extras/gifsteam02-optimized.gif?t=1731513118\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The story</h2><br>The year is 2279, and Enoch stands as humanity's last bastion, where the vast majority of inhabitants live in abject poverty, under the rule of gangs. In this harsh environment, six people are about to meet their fate:<br><br><strong>Arten Long and John Nakanaga</strong> are called to a crime scene, little knowing that this murder will ignite a series of events changing the station's fate forever. How far are they willing to go to solve the case?<br><br><strong>Marcus and Trent Lavergne</strong>, wealthy brothers, face a moral crossroads. Will they do what's right, regardless of the cost?<br><br><strong>Alice Nandi and Swan</strong>, the missing young girl and the killer, find themselves caught in the web of these unfolding events.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086690/extras/gifsteam03.gif?t=1731513118\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A <strong>complex </strong>web of <strong>overlapping storylines</strong>.<br></li><li>Classic <strong>point-and-click</strong> gameplay with a modern interface.<br></li><li><strong>Six playable characters</strong>, each with their own struggles.<br></li><li>Stunning <strong>pixel art</strong> graphics.<br></li><li><strong>Fully voiced</strong> by professional voice actors.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086690/extras/gifsteam01-optimized.gif?t=1731513118\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731513118","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086690/page_bg_ge